Worker Finder is a simple web platform that connects users with local skilled workers like plumbers, carpenters, and electricians. Any registered user can act as both a service seeker and service provider (worker).

🚀 Features
🔧 Users can register as workers by selecting a skill (Plumber, Carpenter, Electrician).

👤 Single account supports both hiring and working roles.

📍 Find nearby workers based on selected service category.

📝 Simple registration & profile management for workers.

🏗️ Technologies Used
Backend: (e.g., Node.js / MongoDB / Express )

Frontend: (e.g., JavaScript / HTML-CSS  )

Database: (e.g., MongoDB / MySQL )

